{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Upgrade the existing regional eSIM tabbed product grid into a premium app-like shopping experience using a hybrid layout:
    
    MOBILE VIEW:
    Use a Slide-Up Bottom Sheet instead of a centered popup modal.
    
    DESKTOP + TABLET VIEW:
    Use a Right-Side Slide Drawer instead of a popup modal.
    
    Do NOT redirect users to the full product page when clicking “Choose Plan”.
    The goal is a fast, premium, mobile-first app-like checkout experience with minimal friction and maximum conversion.
    
    IMPORTANT:
    Keep the existing tabbed grid section exactly as it is (Asia, Europe, Global, Middle East tabs with product cards).
    Only replace the current popup/modal experience with this new Bottom Sheet + Side Drawer hybrid system.
    
    ==================================================
    SECTION REQUIREMENTS
    ==================================================
    
    Each product card must contain:
    - Country flag image
    - Product title
    - Starting price
    - “Choose Plan” button
    
    Product image + Product title:
    - Must be clickable links to the actual product page
    
    Choose Plan button:
    - Must open Bottom Sheet on mobile
    - Must open Right-Side Drawer on desktop
    - Must NOT redirect to product page
    
    ==================================================
    MOBILE UX — BOTTOM SHEET
    ==================================================
    
    On mobile, clicking Choose Plan opens a smooth slide-up Bottom Sheet from the bottom of the screen.
    
    Requirements:
    - Full-width bottom sheet
    - Rounded top corners
    - Drag handle at top
    - Close button (X)
    - Close on outside click
    - Close on swipe down (if possible)
    - Prevent background scrolling while open
    - Smooth open/close animation
    - Lightweight and fast loading
    - Mobile-first optimized for travelers using limited mobile data
    
    ==================================================
    DESKTOP UX — RIGHT SIDE DRAWER
    ==================================================
    
    On desktop/tablet, clicking Choose Plan opens a smooth Right-Side Drawer.
    
    Requirements:
    - Slide in from right side
    - Width around 420–500px
    - Full height
    - Sticky/fixed panel
    - Background page remains visible
    - Close button (X)
    - Close on outside click
    - Smooth transition
    - Premium minimal design
    
    ==================================================
    INSIDE BOTTOM SHEET / DRAWER CONTENT
    ==================================================
    
    TOP HEADER:
    - Product flag image top-left
    - Product title beside image
    - Product price below title
    - Close button top-right
    
    Theme editor settings for popup image:
    - Popup image width
    - Popup image height
    - Popup image object-fit
    - Popup image border radius
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    PRODUCT DESCRIPTION:
    - Show clean short description
    - No broken code
    - No [object Object]
    - No raw Liquid objects
    - No JSON output
    
    Theme settings:
    - Show/hide description
    - Description placement:
      - Above variants
      - Below variants
    - Max description height
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    VARIANT SELECTOR:
    Map Shopify product options by option name:
    
    - “Plan Type” → Plan Type row
    - “Validity” → Validity row
    - “Volume” OR “Data” → Data row
    
    Display variants as premium selectable buttons:
    
    SELECTED:
    - Black background
    - White text
    
    AVAILABLE:
    - White background
    - Black border
    
    OUT OF STOCK:
    - Greyed out
    - Disabled
    - Strikethrough text
    
    Examples:
    
    Plan Type:
    - Day-Pass
    - Total Data
    
    Validity:
    - 1-Day
    - 2-Days
    - 3-Days
    - 5-Days
    - 7-Days
    - 10-Days
    - 15-Days
    - 30-Days
    
    Volume:
    - 1 GB
    - 2 GB
    - 3 GB
    - 5 GB
    - 10GB
    - 15GB
    - 20GB
    - 30GB
    
    Requirements:
    - Selecting options updates selected variant
    - Selecting options updates live price
    - Invalid combinations disabled automatically
    - Out-of-stock variants disabled properly
    - No broken labels like [object Object]
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    QUANTITY SELECTOR:
    Inline quantity stepper:
    
    [-] [1] [+]
    
    Requirements:
    - Minus button
    - Number input
    - Plus button
    - Minimum quantity = 1
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    CTA BUTTONS:
    
    1. Add to Cart
    - Full width
    - Black background
    - White text
    - Use Shopify Ajax Cart API
    - No page reload
    
    2. Buy Now
    - Full width
    - Blue/Navy background
    - White text
    - Add selected variant
    - Redirect directly to checkout
    
    Fast + lightweight required
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    TRUST BADGES SECTION:
    
    Below buttons add premium trust badge section:
    
    Heading:
    “Secure Checkout”
    
    4 badges default:
    - Secure Payment
    - SSL Encrypted
    - Money Back
    - Verified
    
    Theme settings:
    - Show/hide trust badges
    - Badge heading text
    - Badge icons
    - Badge text
    - Badge background color
    - Badge text color
    
    Fully customizable
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    REVIEWS:
    
    Theme settings:
    - Show/hide reviews
    - Reviews placement:
      - Above variants
      - Below variants
      - Below buttons
      - Hidden
    
    Use existing review app block only if available
    Never show broken review code
    
    ==================================================
    THEME EDITOR SETTINGS
    ==================================================
    
    GRID CONTROLS:
    - Desktop p
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-regional-esim-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-tabs-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #666;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    color: {{ block.settings.tab_active_color }};
    border-bottom-color: {{ block.settings.tab_active_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.products_per_row_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-regional-esim-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.products_per_row_mobile }}, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.flag_width }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.flag_height }}px;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.flag_object_fit }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.flag_border_radius }}px;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.product_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.product_title_color }};
    margin: 12px 0 8px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    color: {{ block.settings.tab_active_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.product_price_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.product_price_color }};
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    z-index: 9998;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-bottom-sheet-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.drawer_background }};
    border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translateY(100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    overflow-y: auto;
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-bottom-sheet-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-side-drawer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: {{ block.settings.drawer_width }}px;
    max-width: 90vw;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.drawer_background }};
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translateX(100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    overflow-y: auto;
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-side-drawer-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-regional-esim-bottom-sheet-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-regional-esim-side-drawer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-handle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 40px;
    height: 4px;
    background-color: #d0d0d0;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 12px auto;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.popup_image_width }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.popup_image_height }}px;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.popup_image_object_fit }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.popup_image_border_radius }}px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.drawer_text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.tab_active_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-close-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 8px;
    color: {{ block.settings.drawer_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-drawer-close-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: {{ block.settings.drawer_text_color }};
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-height: {{ block.settings.description_max_height }}px;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variants-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-group-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.drawer_text_color }};
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-options-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.variant_border_radius }}px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #121212;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover:not(.disabled) {
    border-color: {{ block.settings.tab_active_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}.selected {
    background-color: #121212;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-color: #121212;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-variant-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}.disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.drawer_text_color }};
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-selector-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    max-width: 150px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #121212;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-quantity-input-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 50px;
    height: 36px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-cta-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-add-to-cart-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-regional-esim-buy-now-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-add-to-cart-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: #121212;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-add-to-cart-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #000000;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-buy-now-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.buy_now_background }};
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-buy-now-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.buy_now_hover_background }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-trust-badges-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.trust_badge_background }};
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-trust-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_badge_text_color }};
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-trust-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_badge_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-loading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.drawer_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-regional-esim-error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
    padding: 12px;
    background-color: #fee;
    color: #c00;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
{% endstyle %}

<regional-esim-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-regional-esim-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-regional-esim-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-regional-esim-tabs-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.show_asia_tab %}
        <button class="ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }} active" data-tab="asia">
          {{ block.settings.asia_tab_label }}
        </button>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.show_europe_tab %}
        <button class="ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-tab="europe">
          {{ block.settings.europe_tab_label }}
        </button>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.show_global_tab %}
        <button class="ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-tab="global">
          {{ block.settings.global_tab_label }}
        </button>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.show_middle_east_tab %}
        <button class="ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-tab="middle-east">
          {{ block.settings.middle_east_tab_label }}
        </button>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    {% if block.settings.show_asia_tab %}
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} active" data-content="asia">
        <div class="ai-regional-esim-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.asia_collection != blank %}
            {% for product in block.settings.asia_collection.products limit: block.settings.products_limit %}
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <a href="{{ product.url }}">
                    {% if product.featured_image %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                        alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                        class="ai-regional-esim-product-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                        width="400"
                        height="300"
                      >
                    {% endif %}
                  </a>
                </div>
                <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-regional-esim-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ product.title }}
                </a>
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  From {{ product.price | money }}
                </div>
                <button
                  class="ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
                  data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.choose_plan_button_text }}
                </button>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.show_europe_tab %}
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-content="europe">
        <div class="ai-regional-esim-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.europe_collection != blank %}
            {% for product in block.settings.europe_collection.products limit: block.settings.products_limit %}
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <a href="{{ product.url }}">
                    {% if product.featured_image %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                        alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                        class="ai-regional-esim-product-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                        width="400"
                        height="300"
                      >
                    {% endif %}
                  </a>
                </div>
                <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-regional-esim-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ product.title }}
                </a>
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  From {{ product.price | money }}
                </div>
                <button
                  class="ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
                  data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.choose_plan_button_text }}
                </button>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.show_global_tab %}
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-content="global">
        <div class="ai-regional-esim-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.global_collection != blank %}
            {% for product in block.settings.global_collection.products limit: block.settings.products_limit %}
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <a href="{{ product.url }}">
                    {% if product.featured_image %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                        alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                        class="ai-regional-esim-product-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                        width="400"
                        height="300"
                      >
                    {% endif %}
                  </a>
                </div>
                <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-regional-esim-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ product.title }}
                </a>
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  From {{ product.price | money }}
                </div>
                <button
                  class="ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
                  data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.choose_plan_button_text }}
                </button>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.show_middle_east_tab %}
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-content="middle-east">
        <div class="ai-regional-esim-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.middle_east_collection != blank %}
            {% for product in block.settings.middle_east_collection.products limit: block.settings.products_limit %}
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <a href="{{ product.url }}">
                    {% if product.featured_image %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                        alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                        class="ai-regional-esim-product-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                        width="400"
                        height="300"
                      >
                    {% endif %}
                  </a>
                </div>
                <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-regional-esim-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ product.title }}
                </a>
                <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  From {{ product.price | money }}
                </div>
                <button
                  class="ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
                  data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.choose_plan_button_text }}
                </button>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="ai-regional-esim-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>

  <div class="ai-regional-esim-bottom-sheet-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-handle-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
    <div class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-loading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Loading...</div>
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ai-regional-esim-side-drawer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-loading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Loading...</div>
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
      <div class="ai-regional-esim-product-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</regional-esim-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
(function() {
  class RegionalEsimGrid{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
    constructor() {
      super();
      this.tabs = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-regional-esim-tab-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.tabContents = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-regional-esim-tab-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.choosePlanButtons = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-regional-esim-choose-plan-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.overlay = this.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.bottomSheet = this.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-bottom-sheet-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.sideDrawer = this.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-side-drawer-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.currentProduct = null;
      this.selectedVariant = null;
      this.quantity = 1;
      this.showDescription = {{ block.settings.show_description }};
      this.descriptionPlacement = '{{ block.settings.description_placement }}';
      this.showTrustBadges = {{ block.settings.show_trust_badges }};
    }

    connectedCallback() {
      this.setupTabs();
      this.setupChoosePlanButtons();
      this.setupOverlay();
      this.preventBodyScroll();
    }

    setupTabs() {
      this.tabs.forEach(tab => {
        tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
          this.tabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
          this.tabContents.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));
          tab.classList.add('active');
          const tabName = tab.getAttribute('data-tab');
          const content = this.querySelector(`[data-content="${tabName}"]`);
          if (content) {
            content.classList.add('active');
          }
        });
      });
    }

    setupChoosePlanButtons() {
      this.choosePlanButtons.forEach(button => {
        button.addEventListener('click', async (e) => {
          const productHandle = button.getAttribute('data-product-handle');
          await this.openDrawer(productHandle);
        });
      });
    }

    setupOverlay() {
      this.overlay.addEventListener('click', () => {
        this.closeDrawer();
      });
    }

    async openDrawer(productHandle) {
      this.overlay.classList.add('active');
      const drawer = window.innerWidth < 750 ? this.bottomSheet : this.sideDrawer;
      drawer.classList.add('active');
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';

      const loadingEl = drawer.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-loading-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      const errorEl = drawer.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      const detailsEl = drawer.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-product-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

      loadingEl.style.display = 'block';
      errorEl.style.display = 'none';
      detailsEl.innerHTML = '';

      try {
        const response = await fetch(`/products/${productHandle}.js`);
        const product = await response.json();
        this.currentProduct = product;
        this.selectedVariant = product.variants.find(v => v.available) || product.variants[0];
        this.quantity = 1;
        this.renderProductDetails(detailsEl);
        loadingEl.style.display = 'none';
      } catch (error) {
        loadingEl.style.display = 'none';
        errorEl.style.display = 'block';
        errorEl.textContent = 'Failed to load product details. Please try again.';
      }
    }

    closeDrawer() {
      this.overlay.classList.remove('active');
      this.bottomSheet.classList.remove('active');
      this.sideDrawer.classList.remove('active');
      document.body.style.overflow = '';
    }

    renderProductDetails(container) {
      const product = this.currentProduct;
      const variant = this.selectedVariant;

      let html = `
        <div class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <img
            src="${product.featured_image}"
            alt="${product.title}"
            class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-flag-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
          <div class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <h2 class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">${product.title}</h2>
            <div class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-price-display>
              ${this.formatMoney(variant.price)}
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="ai-regional-esim-drawer-close-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Close">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
              <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      `;

      if (this.showDescription && this.descriptionPlacement === 'above_variants' && product.description) {
        html += `
          <div class="ai-regional-esim-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            ${product.description}
          </div>
        `;
      }

      html += this.renderVariants(product);

      if (this.showDescription && this.descriptionPlacement === 'below_variants' && product.description) {
        html += `
          <div class="ai-regional-esim-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            ${product.description}
          </div>
        `;
      }

      html += `
        <div class="ai-regional-esim-quantity-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label class="ai-regional-esim-quantity-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Quantity</label>
          <div class="ai-regional-esim-quantity-selector-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <button class="ai-regional-esim-quantity-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-quantity-decrease ${this.quantity <= 1 ? 'disabled' : ''}>−</button>
            <input
              type="number"
              class="ai-regional-esim-quantity-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              value="${this.quantity}"
              min="1"
              data-quantity-input
            >
            <button class="ai-regional-esim-quantity-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-quantity-increase>+</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-regional-esim-cta-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <button class="ai-regional-esim-add-to-cart-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-add-to-cart>
            Add to Cart
          </button>
          <button class="ai-regional-esim-buy-now-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-buy-now>
            Buy Now
          </button>
        </div>
      `;

      if (this.showTrustBadges) {
        html += `
          <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-badges-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.trust_badge_heading }}</div>
            <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-items-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <svg class="ai-regional-esim-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>{{ block.settings.trust_badge_1_text }}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <svg class="ai-regional-esim-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                  <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>{{ block.settings.trust_badge_2_text }}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <svg class="ai-regional-esim-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                </svg>
                <span>{{ block.settings.trust_badge_3_text }}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-regional-esim-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <svg class="ai-regional-esim-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
                <span>{{ block.settings.trust_badge_4_text }}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        `;
      }

      container.innerHTML = html;
      this.attachDrawerEventListeners(container);
    }

    renderVariants(product) {
      const options = {};
      product.options.forEach((option, index) => {
        const optionName = option.name || option;
        options[optionName] = {
          position: index + 1,
          values: []
        };
      });

      product.variants.forEach(variant => {
        variant.options.forEach((value, index) => {
          const optionName = product.options[index].name || product.options[index];
          if (!options[optionName].values.includes(value)) {
            options[optionName].values.push(value);
          }
        });
      });

      let html = '<div class="ai-regional-esim-variants-{{ ai_gen_id }}">';

      Object.keys(options).forEach(optionName => {
        const normalizedName = optionName.toLowerCase();
        let displayName = optionName;

        if (normalizedName.includes('plan')) {
          displayName = 'Plan Type';
        } else if (normalizedName.includes('validity')) {
          displayName = 'Validity';
        } else if (normalizedName.includes('volume') || normalizedName.includes('data')) {
          displayName = 'Data';
        }

        html += `
          <div class="ai-regional-esim-variant-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label class="ai-regional-esim-variant-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">${displayName}</label>
            <div class="ai-regional-esim-variant-options-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-option-name="${optionName}">
        `;

        options[optionName].values.forEach(value => {
          const isSelected = this.selectedVariant[`option${options[optionName].position}`] === value;
          const isAvailable = this.isOptionAvailable(product, optionName, value);
          const classes = ['ai-regional-esim-variant-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}'];
          if (isSelected) classes.push('selected');
          if (!isAvailable) classes.push('disabled');

          html += `
            <button
              class="${classes.join(' ')}"
              data-option-value="${value}"
              ${!isAvailable ? 'disabled' : ''}
            >
              ${value}
            </button>
          `;
        });

        html += `
            </div>
          </div>
        `;
      });

      html += '</div>';
      return html;
    }

    isOptionAvailable(product, optionName, value) {
      const currentOptions = {};
      product.options.forEach((opt, idx) => {
        const name = opt.name || opt;
        currentOptions[name] = this.selectedVariant[`option${idx + 1}`];
      });

      currentOptions[optionName] = value;

      return product.variants.some(variant => {
        return product.options.every((opt, idx) => {
          const name = opt.name || opt;
          return variant[`option${idx + 1}`] === currentOptions[name];
        }) && variant.available;
      });
    }

    attachDrawerEventListeners(container) {
      const closeBtn = container.querySelector('.ai-regional-esim-drawer-close-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.closeDrawer());

      const variantOptions = container.querySelectorAll('.ai-regional-esim-variant-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      variantOptions.forEach(option => {
        option.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
          if (option.classList.contains('disabled')) return;

          const optionGroup = option.closest('[data-option-name]');
          const optionName = optionGroup.getAttribute('data-option-name');
          const value = option.getAttribute('data-option-value');

          this.updateSelectedVariant(optionName, value);
          this.renderProductDetails(container);
        });
      });

      const decreaseBtn = container.querySelector('[data-quantity-decrease]');
      const increaseBtn = container.querySelector('[data-quantity-increase]');
      const quantityInput = container.querySelector('[data-quantity-input]');

      decreaseBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        if (this.quantity > 1) {
          this.quantity--;
          quantityInput.value = this.quantity;
          decreaseBtn.disabled = this.quantity <= 1;
        }
      });

      increaseBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        this.quantity++;
        quantityInput.value = this.quantity;
        decreaseBtn.disabled = false;
      });

      quantityInput.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
        const value = parseInt(e.target.value);
        if (value >= 1) {
          this.quantity = value;
          decreaseBtn.disabled = this.quantity <= 1;
        } else {
          this.quantity = 1;
          quantityInput.value = 1;
        }
      });

      const addToCartBtn = container.querySelector('[data-add-to-cart]');
      addToCartBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.addToCart());

      const buyNowBtn = container.querySelector('[data-buy-now]');
      buyNowBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.buyNow());
    }

    updateSelectedVariant(optionName, value) {
      const product = this.currentProduct;
      const optionIndex = product.options.findIndex(opt => {
        const name = opt.name || opt;
        return name === optionName;
      });

      const newOptions = {};
      product.options.forEach((opt, idx) => {
        const name = opt.name || opt;
        if (idx === optionIndex) {
          newOptions[`option${idx + 1}`] = value;
        } else {
          newOptions[`option${idx + 1}`] = this.selectedVariant[`option${idx + 1}`];
        }
      });

      const matchingVariant = product.variants.find(variant => {
        return Object.keys(newOptions).every(key => variant[key] === newOptions[key]);
      });

      if (matchingVariant) {
        this.selectedVariant = matchingVariant;
      }
    }

    async addToCart() {
      try {
        const formData = {
          items: [{
            id: this.selectedVariant.id,
            quantity: this.quantity
          }]
        };

        const response = await fetch('/cart/add.js', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: {
            'Content-Type': 'application/json',
          },
          body: JSON.stringify(formData)
        });

        if (response.ok) {
          this.closeDrawer();
          window.dispatchEvent(new Event('cart:refresh'));
        }
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error adding to cart:', error);
      }
    }

    async buyNow() {
      try {
        const formData = {
          items: [{
            id: this.selectedVariant.id,
            quantity: this.quantity
          }]
        };

        const response = await fetch('/cart/add.js', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: {
            'Content-Type': 'application/json',
          },
          body: JSON.stringify(formData)
        });

        if (response.ok) {
          window.location.href = '/checkout';
        }
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error with buy now:', error);
      }
    }

    formatMoney(cents) {
      const amount = cents / 100;
      return new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US', {
        style: 'currency',
        currency: '{{ cart.currency.iso_code }}',
      }).format(amount);
    }

    preventBodyScroll() {
      let startY = 0;
      const drawer = window.innerWidth < 750 ? this.bottomSheet : this.sideDrawer;

      drawer.addEventListener('touchstart', (e) => {
        startY = e.touches[0].clientY;
      });

      drawer.addEventListener('touchmove', (e) => {
        const currentY = e.touches[0].clientY;
        const scrollTop = drawer.scrollTop;
        const isAtTop = scrollTop === 0;
        const isScrollingUp = currentY > startY;

        if (isAtTop && isScrollingUp) {
          e.preventDefault();
        }
      }, { passive: false });
    }
  }

  customElements.define('regional-esim-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}', RegionalEsimGrid{{ ai_gen_id }});
})();
</script>

